       "Lindner M et al. Implementation of expanded newborn screening for LCHAD and VLCAD. J Inherit Metab Dis. 2010;33(Suppl 3):S401–10.",
       "Fingerhut R et al. Evaluation of acylcarnitine ratios for VLCAD screening. Clin Chim Acta. 2010;411(19–20):1520–5.",
       "Diekman EF et al. Fatty-acid oxidation flux analysis in fibroblasts: diagnostic value for long-chain FAO defects. J Inherit Metab Dis. 2015;38(1):73–81.",
       "Andresen BS et al. Clear correlation of genotype with disease phenotype in VLCAD deficiency. Am J Hum Genet. 1999;64(2):479–94.",
       "Gobin-Limballe S et al. Correlation between residual VLCAD activity and the clinical phenotype. Mol Genet Metab. 2010;99(2):150–5.",
       "Souri M et al. Mutation analysis of VLCAD deficiency: identification and characterization of mutant VLCAD cDNAs. Am J Hum Genet. 1996;58(1):97–106.",
       "Laforêt P et al. Late-onset presentations of VLCAD deficiency. J Inherit Metab Dis. 2009;32 Suppl 1:S243–9.",
       "Spiekerkoetter U et al. Treatment recommendations in long-chain fatty acid oxidation defects: consensus from a workshop. J Inherit Metab Dis. 2009;32(4):498–505.",
       "Solis JO, Singh RH. Management of FAO disorders: a survey of current treatment strategies. J Am Diet Assoc. 2002;102(12):1800–3.",
       "Vockley J et al. Triheptanoin treatment in patients with long-chain FAO disorders: phase 2 open-label extension. Mol Genet Metab. 2021;132(3):185–94.",
       "Shirley M. Triheptanoin: first approval. Drugs. 2020;80(15):1595–1600.",
       "Primassin S et al. Carnitine supplementation induces acylcarnitine production in tissues of VLCAD-deficient mice. Pediatr Res. 2008;63(6):632–7.",
       "Pena LDM et al. Outcomes and genotype–phenotype correlations in patients with VLCAD deficiency identified by newborn screening. Mol Genet Metab. 2016;118(4):272–81.",
